acc-opt-but: E aʻo hou e pili ana i nā koho koho
acc-opt-text: Ua pilikia paha ʻoe i ʻole e hiki ke hoʻopau i ka hCaptchas?
appreciate-in: Mahalo mākou i kāu helu. E ʻike iā mākou i kekahi pilikia a e hoʻoponopono koke mākou iā lākou.
fb-but: E hoʻouna i kā mākou noʻonoʻo
feedback-text: Hāʻawi i ka ʻōlelo noʻonoʻo ma ka hCaptcha āu i ʻike ai
learn-more-hcaptcha: Ako mau e pili ana i ka hCaptcha
page-acc-link-1: Inā he mea hoʻohana ʻoe i ka hoʻohana ʻia, e ʻoluʻolu e kākau ma ʻaneʻi.
page-acc-subhead: E hōʻoiaʻiʻo i ka komo pono ʻana no ka mea hoʻohana a pau i ka mālama ʻana i ka palekana
priv-hc-text: E ʻike i nā ʻoihana pūnaewele uila e like me kā lākou huahana. ʻAʻole mākou. ʻAʻole mākou e nānā i nā mea hoʻohana, ʻoiai pehea wale lākou e hōʻino ai. Kākoʻo mākou i nā hana e like me Pass Pass, a hoʻoikaika nui e kūpaʻa i ka pilikino a me ka palekana.
sec-hc-text: hCaptcha kahi mea pili i hoʻopuka. Hana mākou e hāʻawi i nā pūnaewele i nā ʻikepili maoli a e hoʻoholo iā lākou e hoʻohana. ʻO ka pololei ke kūpono a me kā mākou. Hāʻawi ʻia nā captchas e nā hui hoʻolaha. Hiki i kēlā me kēia mea momona ke hōʻemi i kā lākou loaʻa kālā.
what-is-hcaptcha-text: Hāʻawi ka hCaptcha i nā lawelawe pūnaewele punaewele e hūnā i nā bots, spam, a me ka hōʻino ʻana e ka nīnau ʻana i nā nīnau maʻalahi e maʻalahi i nā poʻe a me ka paʻakikī no nā mīkini.
why-hc-text: I kēlā me kēia manawa e pane ʻoe i kahi luʻu, hoʻohana mākou i nā hiʻohiʻona hiʻohiʻona e ʻike ai inā he kanaka ʻoe a he mīkini. ʻO ka pūnaewele āu i kipa ai e hoʻohana i kēia hopena e kōkua i ka hoʻomaikaʻi ʻana i kou ʻike ma kā lākou pūnaewele me ka mālama ʻana i nā bots.
